=================================================================================
                        POWER OPTIMIZATION RECOMMENDATIONS
=================================================================================

1. Implement clock gating for PRBS logic during idle
   Estimated savings: 3.4 mW

2. Reduce SERDES driver swing for shorter PCB traces
   Estimated savings: 2.1 mW

3. Use lower-power I/O standard for LED outputs
   Estimated savings: 0.8 mW

4. Disable RX equalizer when signal quality is good
   Estimated savings: 4.6 mW

5. Implement PLL power-down mode
   Estimated savings: 8.2 mW

Total Potential Savings: 19.1 mW (12.2% reduction)


