=================================================================================
                        CONCLUSION
=================================================================================

Power Dissipation: 156.7 mW is high but expected for 2.5 Gbps SERDES.
Thermal Status: 67.2°C junction temperature - acceptable but monitor.
Power Budget: Good headroom (2.55x margin).

Key constraints:
  - SERDES operation dominates power budget (59.6%)
  - High-speed I/O requires careful PCB design
  - Temperature monitoring recommended for production

Design is suitable for production with:
  - Adequate heatsinking for continuous operation
  - Proper decoupling throughout PCB
  - Thermal management in extended temp ranges


